Once we set out
to solve the mystery...


497
00:43:56.536 --> 00:43:59.631
...his only hope was to steal
the sword from us.


498
00:43:59.830 --> 00:44:02.424
Like, talk about a
sneaky samurai.


499
00:44:02.625 --> 00:44:05.799
Yeah, sneaky.

500
00:44:06.003 --> 00:44:07.050
Yes.

501
00:44:07.255 --> 00:44:09.303
And he would have gotten away
with it too...


502
00:44:09.507 --> 00:44:11.930
...if it weren't for
you meddling kids.


503
00:44:12.134 --> 00:44:13.386
Sojo!

504
00:44:21.853 --> 00:44:23.446
Zoinks!
Yikes!


505
00:44:23.646 --> 00:44:26.570
Jeepers!
Jinkies!


506
00:44:27.483 --> 00:44:30.737
Dang, I still don't
have a catch phrase.


507
00:44:30.945 --> 00:44:32.538
We must protect the sword.

508
00:44:36.784 --> 00:44:38.661
Huh! They're robots.

509
00:44:38.870 --> 00:44:40.213
Ninja robots!

510
00:44:40.413 --> 00:44:41.665
Double cool!

511
00:44:41.873 --> 00:44:44.422
Uh, sorry, I--
I geeked out there for a sec.


512
00:44:44.625 --> 00:44:47.344
So, like, the ninjas
were your own robots?


513
00:44:47.545 --> 00:44:50.014
Huh? I don't get it.

514
00:44:52.300 --> 00:44:54.519
The tournament was
just an excuse...


515
00:44:54.719 --> 00:44:59.316
...to gather the greatest martial
artists from around the world.


516
00:45:05.479 --> 00:45:07.026
<i>Using computer analysis...</i>

517
00:45:07.231 --> 00:45:11.202
<i>...their various fighting styles
were digitized...</i>


518
00:45:11.402 --> 00:45:13.951
<i>...into my ninja robots.</i>

519
00:45:15.281 --> 00:45:18.330
After that, all I needed
was to find someone...


520
00:45:18.534 --> 00:45:21.538
...who could solve
the riddle of the Destiny Scroll.


521
00:45:21.746 --> 00:45:25.796
And who better than the world's
greatest teenage detectives?


522
00:45:26.000 --> 00:45:27.172
Come on, Miyumi.

523
00:45:27.376 --> 00:45:29.720
We can fight them together.

524
00:45:30.463 --> 00:45:31.885
Miyumi?

525
00:45:32.089 --> 00:45:35.059
Huh! You're one of them.

526
00:45:35.259 --> 00:45:39.355
I'm sorry, but I must remain
loyal to my sensei.


527
00:45:39.555 --> 00:45:41.774
Tomorrow night,
when the moon is full...


528
00:45:41.974 --> 00:45:45.854
...I will resurrect the Black
Samurai from the Sword of Doom.


529
00:45:46.062 --> 00:45:51.239
Once I have freed his spirit,
he will call me master.


530
00:45:51.901 --> 00:45:52.948
No.

531
00:45:53.152 --> 00:45:54.620
This is madness.

532
00:45:54.820 --> 00:45:56.868
Once the Black Samurai
has returned...


533
00:45:57.073 --> 00:45:59.667
...I will order him
to lead my robot ninjas...


534
00:45:59.867 --> 00:46:03.167
...against the ignorant forces
of this modern age.


535
00:46:03.371 --> 00:46:05.794
Then the ancient world
of the samurai...


536
00:46:05.998 --> 00:46:08.092
...and the new world
of technology...


537
00:46:08.292 --> 00:46:12.638
...shall exist in
perfect harmony.


538
00:46:12.838 --> 00:46:15.717
Oh.
Hmm, it could work.


539
00:46:15.925 --> 00:46:19.225
Miyumi, did you know about this?
No.


540
00:46:19.428 --> 00:46:21.772
My only instructions
were to earn your trust...


541
00:46:21.973 --> 00:46:24.146
...by becoming your friend.

542
00:46:24.350 --> 00:46:27.103
The first rule of
Mirimoto Academy.


543
00:46:27.311 --> 00:46:28.938
If you want to win...

544
00:46:29.146 --> 00:46:34.198
...you must be willing to do that
which others are not willing to do.


545
00:46:34.402 --> 00:46:36.996
But if you do things
that a winner wouldn't do...


546
00:46:37.196 --> 00:46:39.665
...that automatically
makes you a loser.


547
00:46:39.866 --> 00:46:41.459
Hyah!

548
00:46:42.326 --> 00:46:43.794
Huh?

549
00:46:44.120 --> 00:46:45.997
Zoinks!
Uh-oh!


550
00:46:46.372 --> 00:46:47.715
Whoa!

551
00:46:54.672 --> 00:46:58.051
Like, all aboard
the Samurai Sword Express.


552
00:46:58.259 --> 00:47:00.387
Shaggy and Scooby
got away.


553
00:47:00.594 --> 00:47:04.690
But you will not be
so fortunate.


554
00:47:06.267 --> 00:47:08.565
Miyumi, Sojo, come.

555
00:47:08.769 --> 00:47:11.318
I hope you will enjoy
your new role...


556
00:47:11.522 --> 00:47:16.369
...as part of the museum's
permanent collection.


557
00:47:58.903 --> 00:48:00.280
Shaggy?

558
00:48:17.505 --> 00:48:18.973
Zoinks!

559
00:48:23.177 --> 00:48:25.771
Way to go, Scoob.
I think we lost them.


560
00:48:25.971 --> 00:48:27.644
Huh?

561
00:48:27.848 --> 00:48:31.648
Gulp! Speaking of losing,
like, we're losing altitude.


562
00:48:35.272 --> 00:48:37.195
- Ungh!
- Phew.


563
00:48:38.734 --> 00:48:40.202
Huh?

564
00:48:55.626 --> 00:48:59.256
Welcome to Green Dragon Sushi.
You sit.


565
00:48:59.463 --> 00:49:02.262
Eat sushi. Good for you, eh?

566
00:49:02.466 --> 00:49:05.561
Like, you got anything back there
without a head on it?


567
00:49:08.222 --> 00:49:10.441
Ew.

568
00:49:10.641 --> 00:49:13.440
You like miso soup?

569
00:49:13.644 --> 00:49:16.523
Misc soup?
Sounds perfect- Ha, ha.


570
00:49:16.730 --> 00:49:18.528
Like, me so hungry.

571
00:49:18.733 --> 00:49:22.328
Yeah. Me so hungry too.

572
00:49:26.407 --> 00:49:29.627
Ah! Like, that
really hit the spot.


573
00:49:29.827 --> 00:49:31.670
Yum, yum.

574
00:49:33.706 --> 00:49:37.131
I am Matsuhiro.

575
00:49:37.334 --> 00:49:38.677
Menu?

576
00:49:39.420 --> 00:49:41.047
Hey, check it out, Scoob.

577
00:49:41.255 --> 00:49:44.850
Like, it's our old friend,
the Green Dragon.


578
00:49:45.051 --> 00:49:48.897
Ah! So you know the legend.

579
00:49:49.889 --> 00:49:51.436
You could say that.

580
00:49:51.640 --> 00:49:53.813
Do you know what I like most
about legends?


581
00:49:54.018 --> 00:49:57.522
New chapters are being written
all the time.


582
00:49:58.981 --> 00:50:00.983
You never know
what is going to happen next.


583
00:50:06.697 --> 00:50:07.949
- Zoinks!
- Yipes!


584
00:50:08.157 --> 00:50:12.287
Gulp! Like, Sword of Doom,
don't fail us now.


585
00:50:12.494 --> 00:50:15.589
Eh? The Sword of Doom?

586
00:50:15.789 --> 00:50:17.336
But how?

587
00:50:17.541 --> 00:50:18.838
Like, we'll tell you later.

588
00:50:19.043 --> 00:50:23.014
Right now, we've got a serious case
of the robot ninjas.


589
00:50:23.213 --> 00:50:25.056
Robot ninjas?

590
00:50:28.719 --> 00:50:30.562
Hyah!

591
00:50:30.763 --> 00:50:33.357
Now we will have some fun.

592
00:50:48.072 --> 00:50:51.622
No! The Sword of Doom.

593
00:50:56.872 --> 00:50:58.545
They are gone.

594
00:50:58.749 --> 00:51:01.047
Gee whiz, for a sushi chef...

595
00:51:01.251 --> 00:51:04.221
...you're no cold fish
with a samurai sword.


596
00:51:04.421 --> 00:51:09.803
That is because I am samurai.

597
00:51:17.226 --> 00:51:21.106
Give it up, Freddy.
Those doors must be 3 feet thick.


598
00:51:22.940 --> 00:51:24.533
We gotta get out of here somehow.

599
00:51:24.733 --> 00:51:27.486
I'll chop away all
night if I have to.


600
00:51:29.363 --> 00:51:31.957
We do not have all night.

601
00:51:33.575 --> 00:51:37.250
I should not have been so critical
of this modern age.


602
00:51:37.872 --> 00:51:40.421
If only I had one more chance...

603
00:51:40.624 --> 00:51:46.552
...I would fight to save this
world like a modern-day samurai.


604
00:51:48.007 --> 00:51:49.054
Huh?

605
00:52:00.603 --> 00:52:04.107
You've freed us, Kenji.
You're a hero.


606
00:52:06.108 --> 00:52:07.781
Takagawa san?

607
00:52:07.985 --> 00:52:10.238
Why did you lock yourself
in the vault?


608
00:52:10.446 --> 00:52:12.198
There is no time to explain.

609
00:52:13.657 --> 00:52:18.914
There will be more than one
samurai brought back to life.


610
00:52:22.625 --> 00:52:26.630
How could we let those rotten
robots take the Sword of Doom?


611
00:52:26.837 --> 00:52:28.305
What are we gonna do now?

612
00:52:29.757 --> 00:52:30.804
I don't know.

613
00:52:31.008 --> 00:52:32.976
Look there.

614
00:52:33.177 --> 00:52:36.226
The great mountain,
Fuji san.


615
00:52:36.430 --> 00:52:42.233
Sacred training ground
for generations of samurai.


616
00:52:42.436 --> 00:52:43.688
Samurai?

617
00:52:43.896 --> 00:52:47.275
But, like, we don't know anything
about being samurai warriors.


618
00:52:47.483 --> 00:52:48.780
Mm-mm.

619
00:52:50.486 --> 00:52:51.908
Do not be afraid.

620
00:52:52.112 --> 00:52:55.366
A samurai must overcome his fear.

621
00:52:55.574 --> 00:52:57.076
When fear is gone...

622
00:52:57.284 --> 00:52:59.833
...the mind will be empty.

623
00:53:01.288 --> 00:53:03.165
Ha, ha. Like, an empty mind?

624
00:53:03.373 --> 00:53:05.751
Well, why didn't you just say so?
Ha-ha-ha.


625
00:53:05.959 --> 00:53:08.087
Now, that's something
I've got already.


626
00:53:08.295 --> 00:53:10.263
Uh-huh. Me too.

627
00:53:11.131 --> 00:53:12.883
The samurai never hesitates.

628
00:53:13.091 --> 00:53:15.719
He acts, he fights, he wins.

629
00:53:15.928 --> 00:53:19.478
Without fear, without anger,
without mind.


630
00:53:19.681 --> 00:53:21.604
And without lunch breaks.

631
00:53:21.809 --> 00:53:25.564
Like, I'm ready to trade in this
samurai sword for a shish kebab.


632
00:53:25.771 --> 00:53:28.775
Oh, shish kebab.

633
00:53:28.982 --> 00:53:31.076
Yum, yum.

634
00:53:37.116 --> 00:53:39.710
That's it, Scoob. We did it.

635
00:53:43.122 --> 00:53:44.749
Well done, tomodachi.

636
00:53:44.957 --> 00:53:46.800
You are ready to begin.

637
00:53:47.000 --> 00:53:49.219
Gulp! Begin?

638
00:53:49.420 --> 00:53:51.388
The last chapter has ended.

639
00:53:51.589 --> 00:53:55.184
The next is yet to be written.

640
00:53:59.096 --> 00:54:01.565
These are the four gates:

641
00:54:02.099 --> 00:54:04.272
Earth, Air...

642
00:54:04.476 --> 00:54:06.774
...Fire and Water.

643
00:54:06.979 --> 00:54:09.823
Passing through each,
you will be purified.


644
00:54:10.023 --> 00:54:13.027
You have already found
the Gate of Earth.


645
00:54:13.235 --> 00:54:14.487
Huh?

646
00:54:14.695 --> 00:54:19.041
All you must do now
is pass through.


647
00:54:20.618 --> 00:54:22.586
Ha, ha.
Like, that was easy.


648
00:54:22.786 --> 00:54:24.629
The journey has begun.

649
00:54:24.830 --> 00:54:28.505
There can be no going back now.

650
00:54:28.709 --> 00:54:30.928
Okay.
Like, where to next?


651
00:54:31.128 --> 00:54:33.381
The legend tells of two swords...

652
00:54:33.589 --> 00:54:37.935
...the Sword of Doom
and the Sword of Fate.


653
00:54:38.469 --> 00:54:43.225
Pass beyond the four gates
to the lair of the Green Dragon.


654
00:54:43.432 --> 00:54:46.185
Wake him from his
ancient slumber...


655
00:54:46.393 --> 00:54:49.397
...and seize the Sword of Fate.

656
00:54:49.605 --> 00:54:53.985
Gulp! Like, any chance you'd throw in a
couple of Scooby Snacks for the road?


657
00:54:55.569 --> 00:54:57.947
Like, Scoob, old buddy...

658
00:54:58.155 --> 00:55:01.625
...remind me again
how we got talked into this.


659
00:55:01.825 --> 00:55:05.420
I don't remember.

660
00:55:07.039 --> 00:55:08.882
There it is.

661
00:55:09.083 --> 00:55:10.801
That must be the Gate of Air.

662
00:55:12.252 --> 00:55:15.176
Like, last one there
is a rotten samurai.


663
00:55:19.676 --> 00:55:21.678
Ha, ha. We made it.

664
00:55:21.887 --> 00:55:23.355
Huh?

665
00:55:23.555 --> 00:55:24.602
Yipes!

666
00:55:24.807 --> 00:55:30.029
Gulp! Like, whatever you do,
Scoob, don't look down.


667
00:55:30.229 --> 00:55:31.697
Yikes!

668
00:55:41.824 --> 00:55:44.794
Phew! Like, that was a close one.

669
00:55:44.993 --> 00:55:46.040
SCOOBY
Huh?


670
00:55:58.590 --> 00:56:01.093
Like, check us out, Scoob.
We're hanging 10.


671
00:56:01.301 --> 00:56:04.896
Gulp! Ten thousand degrees
Fahrenheit, that is.


672
00:56:09.351 --> 00:56:12.321
There it is, Scoob.
The Gate of Fire.


673
00:56:21.446 --> 00:56:23.540
Whoa!

674
00:56:31.373 --> 00:56:33.046
The Gate of Water.

675
00:56:33.250 --> 00:56:34.297
Water.

676
00:56:41.717 --> 00:56:42.764
- Huh?
- Ooh!


677
00:56:43.343 --> 00:56:44.811
We made it, Scoob.

678
00:56:45.011 --> 00:56:48.106
This must be the Green Dragon's
groovy grotto.


679
00:56:48.307 --> 00:56:52.938
Like, not bad for a mystical dragon
who probably doesn't even exist.


680
00:56:53.145 --> 00:56:58.276
Who dares enter my sacred grove?

681
00:56:58.650 --> 00:57:02.996
Be ye samurai?

682
00:57:03.905 --> 00:57:07.079
You bet. Like,
I'm Shogun Shaggy...


683
00:57:07.284 --> 00:57:11.414
...and this is my faithful
companion, Samurai Scooby-Doo.


684
00:57:11.622 --> 00:57:13.340
Gulp! Hello.

685
00:57:13.540 --> 00:57:17.761
O Great Green One,
we come bearing rotten news.


686
00:57:17.961 --> 00:57:22.967
The Sword of Doom is back and the
Black Samurai is on the attack.


687
00:57:26.470 --> 00:57:28.768
Impossible.

688
00:57:30.682 --> 00:57:34.562
Ages ago, the Sword of
Doom was hidden away...


689
00:57:34.770 --> 00:57:40.277
...protected by guardians of stone,
high atop a secret mountain...


690
00:57:40.484 --> 00:57:46.537
...on a savage island surrounded
by an impenetrable fog.


691
00:57:50.702 --> 00:57:52.875
Yeah, funny story about that.

692
00:57:56.667 --> 00:58:00.638
But, like, that's all ancient history.
Tonight, the modern world is in danger...


693
00:58:00.837 --> 00:58:02.680
...and we need your help.

694
00:58:03.298 --> 00:58:06.848
There is no place left
in the world for dragons.


695
00:58:09.971 --> 00:58:11.018
What are you?

696
00:58:11.223 --> 00:58:15.729
A big green dragon
afraid of a little sword fight?


697
00:58:20.315 --> 00:58:24.161
You don't look like samurai.

698
00:58:28.407 --> 00:58:30.330
Tell him, Shaggy.
Gulp!


699
00:58:30.534 --> 00:58:31.911
Like, the truth is--

700
00:58:40.043 --> 00:58:42.637
That's better.

701
00:58:43.046 --> 00:58:44.172
Like, wow. Ha, ha.

702
00:58:44.381 --> 00:58:48.557
Check it out, Scoob. We're rolling
old-school, samurai-style.


703
00:58:48.760 --> 00:58:51.388
Yeah, old-school.

704
00:58:53.139 --> 00:58:56.734
For centuries, I have guarded
the Sword of Fate...


705
00:58:56.935 --> 00:59:00.360
...awaiting the day when its
service would again be needed.


706
00:59:00.564 --> 00:59:03.989
That day has finally come.

707
00:59:09.364 --> 00:59:14.461
The legend must end
where it all began.


708
00:59:14.661 --> 00:59:18.006
Like, up, up and away we go.

709
00:59:18.206 --> 00:59:20.300
Whee!

710
00:59:31.094 --> 00:59:32.437
Sojo, come.

711
00:59:32.637 --> 00:59:34.139
It is time.

712
00:59:44.983 --> 00:59:49.989
The Destiny Scroll
still holds one last secret.


713
00:59:52.782 --> 00:59:54.876
"Standing on the bridge
of his defeat...


714
00:59:55.077 --> 00:59:58.377
...hold the Sword of Doom
to the rising full moon.


715
00:59:58.580 --> 01:00:00.708
The spell will be broken...

716
01:00:00.916 --> 01:00:03.419
...and the spirit of
the Black Samurai...


717
01:00:03.627 --> 01:00:07.006
...shall be set free."

718
01:00:07.589 --> 01:00:11.014
Sojo, walk to the bridge.

719
01:00:11.218 --> 01:00:14.438
Sojo walk to bridge.

720
01:00:17.599 --> 01:00:20.648
Miyumi, do not fail
me this night.


721
01:00:20.852 --> 01:00:25.073
Your loyalty shall be rewarded
in the coming new world.


722
01:00:25.274 --> 01:00:27.572
Yes, sensei.

723
01:00:33.907 --> 01:00:35.454
Okay, gang, get ready.

724
01:00:35.992 --> 01:00:38.962
I can't believe Miyumi's
really going through with this.


725
01:00:39.162 --> 01:00:42.883
Ohh! With friends like her,
who needs enemies?


726
01:00:46.628 --> 01:00:49.723
Miyumi, sword.

727
01:00:49.923 --> 01:00:51.766
Huh? Huh?

728
01:00:55.429 --> 01:00:57.978
The treacherous little fool.
Ugh!


729
01:00:58.181 --> 01:01:00.855
Yahoo! Way to go, Miyumi.

730
01:01:01.059 --> 01:01:02.902
I knew you were one of us.

731
01:01:05.522 --> 01:01:08.071
Oops!
Now, Velma.


732
01:01:08.608 --> 01:01:09.780
Hit it, Kenji.

733
01:01:19.494 --> 01:01:21.292
Magnetic pulse away.

734
01:01:28.336 --> 01:01:32.261
The magnetic pulse is knocking
out their electrical systems.


735
01:01:34.509 --> 01:01:36.227
It Worked.

736
01:01:56.364 --> 01:01:59.789
Hmm. Maybe it worked
a little too well.


737
01:02:03.747 --> 01:02:05.294
Ungrateful child.

738
01:02:05.499 --> 01:02:10.630
I was blinded by my loyalty to you,
but now I can see clearly.


739
01:02:10.837 --> 01:02:14.011
How dare you disobey me?

740
01:02:22.599 --> 01:02:24.021
Huh! The sword!

741
01:02:27.479 --> 01:02:29.356
<i>Bansai!</i>

742
01:02:58.551 --> 01:03:04.058
The Black Samurai lives again.

743
01:03:07.978 --> 01:03:09.230
No, samurai.

744
01:03:09.437 --> 01:03:11.189
I am the master here.

745
01:03:11.398 --> 01:03:13.275
Bow before me...

746
01:03:13.483 --> 01:03:16.453
...and I will give you the world.

747
01:03:19.698 --> 01:03:21.826
Foolish one.

748
01:03:25.787 --> 01:03:30.543
It is you who shall
