753
01:03:52.230 --> 01:03:54.983
All shall serve me...

754
01:03:55.191 --> 01:03:57.944
...forever!

755
01:04:02.198 --> 01:04:04.200
Shaggy, look.

756
01:04:09.664 --> 01:04:14.670
At last, freedom is mine.

757
01:04:14.878 --> 01:04:17.097
Oh, no. Like, we're too late.

758
01:04:17.297 --> 01:04:18.344
Fear not.

759
01:04:18.548 --> 01:04:21.677
Shogun Shaggy, 
Samurai Scooby...

760
01:04:21.885 --> 01:04:24.434
...you must carry on the fight.

761
01:04:24.637 --> 01:04:26.981
Unsheathe the Sword of Fate...

762
01:04:27.182 --> 01:04:31.062
...so that my spirit
may enter the blade.


763
01:04:31.269 --> 01:04:34.022
I shall be with you always...

764
01:04:34.230 --> 01:04:39.282
...guiding the sword from within.

765
01:04:50.246 --> 01:04:51.714
Guys, look.

766
01:04:51.915 --> 01:04:53.758
Huh! It's Shaggy and Scooby.

767
01:04:53.958 --> 01:04:55.460
Ow! My neck.

768
01:04:56.878 --> 01:04:59.973
Like, right on time,
late as usual.


769
01:05:11.309 --> 01:05:16.065
Who dares challenge
the Black Samurai?


770
01:05:16.272 --> 01:05:18.400
Zoinks!
Like, here we go, Scoob.


771
01:05:18.608 --> 01:05:21.327
Remember what they taught us
in samurai school.


772
01:05:21.528 --> 01:05:24.407
Uh... Uh, I forgot.

773
01:05:33.456 --> 01:05:35.208
Huh?

774
01:05:35.959 --> 01:05:38.712
The Sword of Fate?

775
01:05:39.462 --> 01:05:41.089
Impossible.

776
01:05:41.297 --> 01:05:43.049
Like, you think
that's impossible...


777
01:05:43.258 --> 01:05:46.728
...try flying into Tokyo
on a green dragon sometime.


778
01:06:33.558 --> 01:06:34.935
Hyah!

779
01:06:48.406 --> 01:06:51.205
Fools. You are no match for me.

780
01:06:53.912 --> 01:06:55.664
- Aah!
- Yipes!


781
01:06:58.791 --> 01:07:02.216
A samurai must overcome his fear.

782
01:07:02.420 --> 01:07:07.802
When fear is gone,
the mind will be empty.


783
01:07:08.009 --> 01:07:09.886
Like, did you hear that, Scoob?

784
01:07:10.094 --> 01:07:12.347
Yeah, I did.

785
01:07:12.555 --> 01:07:15.024
It's that sushi sword master,
Matsuhiro.


786
01:07:15.224 --> 01:07:16.396
He's in my head.

787
01:07:16.601 --> 01:07:18.695
No, I'm not. I'm over here.

788
01:07:18.895 --> 01:07:22.024
The samurai acts without anger.

789
01:07:22.231 --> 01:07:24.905
He fights without mind.

790
01:07:29.781 --> 01:07:30.828
Yikes!

791
01:07:31.032 --> 01:07:33.000
Don't think, Scoob.
Just let it go.


792
01:07:33.201 --> 01:07:35.203
Like, no mind.

793
01:07:35.411 --> 01:07:37.539
Oh, yeah.

794
01:07:38.915 --> 01:07:44.422
The Sword of Doom
shall be your destroyer.


795
01:07:54.430 --> 01:07:55.977
Hyah!

796
01:07:59.769 --> 01:08:04.024
No!

797
01:08:17.495 --> 01:08:21.170
Ha, ha. Like, that psychotic
samurai forgot one thing.


798
01:08:21.374 --> 01:08:24.628
When it comes to no mind,
we've got everybody beat.


799
01:08:24.836 --> 01:08:26.759
Like, our minds are
always empty.


800
01:08:26.963 --> 01:08:28.590
Yeah.

801
01:08:30.425 --> 01:08:33.850
Scooby, Shaggy,
that was amazing.


802
01:08:38.057 --> 01:08:39.149
Huh?

803
01:08:45.773 --> 01:08:48.572
Like, it's just a little old man.

804
01:08:48.776 --> 01:08:50.119
Thank you...

805
01:08:50.320 --> 01:08:53.915
...most honored friends.

806
01:08:54.115 --> 01:08:56.163
You have released my spirit...

807
01:08:56.367 --> 01:09:00.747
...from the evil power
of that cursed sword...


808
01:09:00.955 --> 01:09:03.799
...and saved your world.

809
01:09:04.000 --> 01:09:08.927
I shall be eternally grateful.

810
01:09:09.130 --> 01:09:12.930
You are indeed samurai...

811
01:09:13.134 --> 01:09:16.638
...and your legend
shall be told...


812
01:09:17.346 --> 01:09:20.065
...forever.

813
01:09:23.478 --> 01:09:24.525
Wow.

814
01:09:24.729 --> 01:09:26.106
He disappeared.

815
01:09:26.314 --> 01:09:28.112
Well, you gotta hand it to him.

816
01:09:28.316 --> 01:09:31.115
He went out in real
samurai-style.


817
01:09:33.404 --> 01:09:34.747
Congratulations...

818
01:09:35.448 --> 01:09:37.917
...samurai.

819
01:09:38.659 --> 01:09:43.085
The last chapter of the legend
has finally been written...


820
01:09:43.289 --> 01:09:45.963
"by you.

821
01:09:48.127 --> 01:09:49.549
<i>Welcome to...</i>

822
01:09:49.754 --> 01:09:51.848
<i>...the new Tokyo Museum
of Cultural History...</i>


823
01:09:52.048 --> 01:09:55.769
<i>...and the grand opening
of our most legendary exhibit...</i>


824
01:09:55.969 --> 01:10:00.315
<i>...the ghost of the
Black Samurai.</i>


825
01:10:00.932 --> 01:10:04.311
And so, it is with
great honor that I present...


826
01:10:04.519 --> 01:10:09.946
...for loyal service to his friends,
to Japan and to all the world...


827
01:10:10.149 --> 01:10:12.618
...this statue...

828
01:10:12.860 --> 01:10:16.956
...in honor of Scooby
-Doo.

829
01:10:22.078 --> 01:10:25.127
Droo-ga-ga. Droo-ga-ga.

830
01:10:28.668 --> 01:10:31.717
Scoob, you really did get
your own statue.


831
01:10:31.921 --> 01:10:34.549
Ha, ha. And, like,
they even got your good side.


832
01:10:34.757 --> 01:10:35.974
Yeah.

833
01:10:37.427 --> 01:10:40.226
Ha, ha. Congratulations, Scooby.

834
01:10:41.014 --> 01:10:44.814
Now Japan will
remember you forever.


835
01:10:45.018 --> 01:10:47.487
Are you sure you won't come
with us, Miyumi?


836
01:10:47.687 --> 01:10:50.236
There's bound to be other
mysteries that need solving.


837
01:10:50.439 --> 01:10:53.067
And there's always room for one
more in the Mystery Machine.


838
01:10:53.276 --> 01:10:55.950
Yeah, like, you could sit
in the back with me and Scooby.


839
01:10:56.154 --> 01:10:58.202
Yeah, sit with me.

840
01:10:58.698 --> 01:11:00.325
You're all very sweet...

841
01:11:00.533 --> 01:11:02.661
...but solving mysteries
is what you do best.


842
01:11:02.869 --> 01:11:05.998
Now I need to figure out
what it is that I do best.


843
01:11:06.206 --> 01:11:07.423
Then maybe someday...

844
01:11:07.623 --> 01:11:10.297
...I will have what it takes
to become a legend too.


845
01:11:10.501 --> 01:11:12.299
Just like you, Scooby.

846
01:11:14.297 --> 01:11:15.844
Aw...

847
01:11:23.639 --> 01:11:25.687
Heh, heh. Oh, brother.

848
01:11:25.892 --> 01:11:27.064
This could take a while.

849
01:11:28.519 --> 01:11:31.773
We may just have to leave Scooby
here and take the statue home.


850
01:11:37.320 --> 01:11:41.621
Scooby
-Dooby
-Doo!